Text: "It\u2019s a story about a 85 year old woman decided to write her diaries when\
  \ she felt that life was coming to an end. She used to work for a hospital as a\
  \ (a job like a nurse but it\u2019s not literally a nurse). Her job responsibilities\
  \ were to help the patients who was suffering from any serious diseases or psychiatric\
  \ illness to overcome their difficulties, which gave her an opportunity to meet\
  \ lots of different stories of different people in one place."
